        "details": " <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n<p>The <b>buff-barred warbler</b> (<i>Phylloscopus pulcher</i>) is a species of leaf warbler (family Phylloscopidae). It was formerly included in the \"Old World warbler\" assemblage.\n</p><p>It is found in Bhutan, China, India, Laos, Myanmar, Nepal, Thailand, and Vietnam. Its natural habitats are boreal forests and temperate forests.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n\n\n<p><br></p>"
